{"tid":658185,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[本地band]Ashley@⼩紅帽,刹那樂團,Mr. rocket hand仲有多隊band會係5月20唱爆浪潮音樂","createTime":"2018-05-08T18:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T18:50:14.000Z","uid":45622,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"72fa13f1a61c188f1364a876a2f905c20e9224c1","tid":658185,"uid":45622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T18:07:33.000Z","msg":"因為香港本地樂隊比較小人認識<br />\n所以我地拍咗一套以香港本地樂隊為題嘅電影<br />\n除咗電影,還會於5月20日舉辦一場音樂放映會<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/020620_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F020620_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bd1f77dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lt;守破離《變調．休止符》首映音樂會&gt;<br />\n<br />\n香港小有的電影首映音樂會，不僅有Kit Lo@逆流 NiLiu，Ashley@小紅帽，Sai Kit Ho @SEESAW，Pigson Kwok@剎那樂團 主演的獨立電影《變調．休止符》借此宣傳香港獨立音樂。<br />\n<br />\n更聚合香港最強的獨立樂隊包括 Nowhere boys，Mr. Rocket head，剎那樂團 KSANA，Ashley@小紅帽，享樂團3think，Sad Jay等多隊樂隊。每隊確保有40分鐘的時間，唱爆浪潮音樂！！<br />\n<br />\n守破離代表著獨立音樂一個不一樣的意思。<br />\n<br />\n「守」，安分守已，學習一切舊有保守香港音樂風格，練習基本功直到熟練，學習各種理論重要。 <br />\n「破」，破舊立新，開始打破舊有的音樂思想，從而因地制宜靈活運用。 <br />\n「離」，影形不離，離開平庸俗世的音樂，超越所有規範的限制。自立門戶，修練新一代香港獨立音樂的境界。<br />\n<br />\n那次活動和電影是學生全自資籌辦，在收入當中我們會扣除成本支出後全數捐出到 Music Children Foundation 音樂兒童基金會。香港樂迷們絕對不能錯過，合力將現場塞滿，希望親身支持香港獨立音樂！<br />\n<br />\nLine Up :  <br />\n剎那樂團<br />\nAshley Tsang @小紅帽<br />\nNowhere Boys<br />\nMr. Rocket Head 火箭頭先生樂團<br />\n享樂團3Think<br />\nSAD JAY<br />\n<br />\n日期: 2018年5月20日<br />\n時間: 晚上7:00-11:00<br />\n地點: 浪潮音樂 Wave Music HK <br />\n地址: 香港九龍觀塘道470號觀塘工業中心二期地庫F&amp;G室 <br />\n票價 (全場企位): <br />\n$100 (預售)<br />\n$120 (即場)<br />\n<br />\n網上預售票現已在 <a href=\"http://thepointofsale.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthepointofsale.hk&d=YutFC7m1wFMtogwEPGPStwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=e64f4a72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">thepointofsale.hk</a> 發售<br />\n<br />\n購買門票 : <a href=\"https://thepointofsale.hk/tickets/mth180521001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthepointofsale.hk%2Ftickets%2Fmth180521001&d=YutFC7m1wFMtogwEPGPStwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=20320f04\" target=\"_blank\">https://thepointofsale.hk/tickets/mth180521001</a><br />\n<br />\n電影預告：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MusicTalkerHK/videos/821179298090405/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMusicTalkerHK%2Fvideos%2F821179298090405%2F%20&d=YutFC7m1wFMtogwEPGPStwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=80f04636\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MusicTalkerHK/videos/821179298090405/ </a><br />\n<br />\n#小紅帽 #silhungmo #MrRockethead #火箭頭先生樂團 #Nowhereboys<br />\n#享樂團 #3think #SadJay #剎那樂團 #KSANA<br />\n#逆流 #niliuhk #Seesaw <br />\n#WaveMusicHK #浪潮音樂"},{"pid":"75c702db4ad32bd97691b61165296126b5c1a9bc","tid":658185,"uid":66270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T23:09:54.000Z","msg":"哇咁多對band 正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9f31ed0e6fcee6e9fd37c6b40f861b0cd21f23","tid":658185,"uid":45622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哇咁多對band 正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地都好支持我地用咁嘅方式去話俾大眾知香港仲有其他好音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港玩音樂已經夠難,受人喜愛,支持更難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快d支持下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7eb5ffd0677e4b1abee762a2e0d09f0e90e2510","tid":658185,"uid":45622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e050884fc0e308e9ba174657762951e02a8f2ee","tid":658185,"uid":45622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fro